Initial scaffold: The Schematic Archive

Astro 5 static site with a Preact filter island, GitHub-backed JSON data,
and three sample entries.

Includes:
- Manifest JSON schema with controlled vocabularies (category, tier,
  footprint, modes, dlc, themes, game version).
- src/site-config.ts with display labels, DLC release order, sort/bucket
  definitions. (TODO: confirm DLC release order.)
- BaseLayout + BuildLayout + BuildCard, ScreenshotCarousel, MetaPanel,
  DownloadButton, TagChip.
- GalleryBrowser.tsx (Preact island): tabs (Featured/Recent/All), search
  via MiniSearch, filter rail with live "if I add this" counts, sort,
  URL-encoded state.
- Pages: /, /browse, /submit, /about, /entry/[slug].
- scripts/build-index.mjs (glob manifests, write gallery-index.json and
  search-index.json, copy assets to public/entry-assets/).
- scripts/validate-manifests.mjs (CI: ajv schema check plus asset existence).
- GitHub issue templates (submit-entry, report-entry).
- GitHub Actions: validate-pr.yml, deploy.yml (Pages).
- Three sample entries: Frostbound Keep (featured, T3, Castlevania +
  Sinister Evolution), Humble Outpost (T1 vanilla), Emerald Garden
  (featured, T2, Dracula's Relics, garden theme).

Verified: pnpm install OK, build-index OK, validate OK, astro build OK
(7 pages, sitemap generated).

